snippet.title: Lupita Nyong'o Conquered Her Fear Of Heights While Filming 'The 355'
snippet.description:
While catching up with ET Canada's Carlos Bustamante, Lupita Nyong'o recalls how jumping from one floor to another during filming for her new spy movie, "The 355", helped her to overcome her fear of heights.
